data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern living and eco-friendliness in this meticulously maintained property in Kissimmee, Florida, built in 2017. Nestled in a serene and friendly community, this inviting home offers not just a house but a lifestyle. With its prime location, you're just moments away from major highways, making your daily commute a breeze. Enjoy proximity to shopping malls, grocery stores, top-rated schools, and a quick 35-minute drive to Orlando's world-famous theme parks. This property is not just about location; it's about sustainability too, featuring solar panels that significantly reduce energy costs and will be fully paid at closing. From the immaculate landscaping to the flawless interior, this home reflects pride of ownership and offers a haven of comfort and sophistication. Come and discover the endless possibilities that await you. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this your dream home.
